Write a program to create a sequential data file named
"record.txt" and store Roll number, Name, Address, and Class of
few students.
OPEN "record.txt" FOR OUTPUT AS #1
CLS
DO
    INPUT "Enter roll, name, address, and class of a student: "; r, n$, a$, c
    WRITE #1, r, n$, a$, c
    INPUT "Do you want to continue? "; x$
LOOP WHILE UCASE$(x$) = "Y"
CLOSE #1
END
        
